          "TITLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Investigation of states in 17O via",
                "neutron-polarization measurements in the",
                "13C(alpha,n)16O reaction"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "AUTHOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "W.L.Baker",
                "C.E.Busch",
                "J.A.Keane",
                "T.R.Donoghue"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INSTITUTE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "1USAOSU"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "REFERENCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "code": "J,PR/C,3,494,1971",
                "code_unit": [
                  {
                    "unit": "J,PR/C,3,494,1971",
                    "doi": "10.1103/PhysRevC.3.494",
                    "field": {
                      "reference_type": "J",
                      "reference": {
                        "code": "PR/C",
                        "number": null,
                        "volume": "3",
                        "part": null,
                        "issue": null,
                        "page": "494"
                      },
                      "date": 1971
                    }
                  }
                ],
                "unit_combination": "(%)"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "#doi:10.1103/PhysRevC.3.494"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The neutrons scattered through 121 degrees (lab) from",
                "a high- pressure helium gas scintillator (180-atm He,",
                "20- atm Xe) are detected by either of two 3x2x6-in.",
                "Pilot-B plastic neutron detectors."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The targets were made by cracking methyl iodide onto",
                "hot 0.005-in. -thick tantalum disks. The target",
                "thicknesses, determined by measuring the yield of the",
                "13C(p,gamma)14N reaction over the narrow resonance at",
                "Ep= 1.75 MeV, ranged 20 to 80 mu-g/cm2."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "nuclide": "6-C-13",
                "field_identifier": "ENR",
                "value": 0.55
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COINC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            }
          ],
          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Corrections to the pulse-height spectra were made for",
                "background counts arising from accidental coincidences",
                " (0.5% contribution) and true coincidences due to",
                "indirect neutrons from the target (2% contribution).",
                "A small correction to the asymmetry was also made in",
                "several of the measurements for incomplete precession",
                "of the neutron spins."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "HISTORY": [
